text:
NOT WORTH THE WAIT!
Me and my friends waited for >1h for our wings for dinner at the shop itself. Can tell the staff couldnâ€™t cope with the huge influx of online & Grab orders with many upset Grab drivers & customers

Wings: While they were juicy and tender, I think Louisiana flavor is not bad but the Garlic Parmesan leaves a lot to be desired. Not enough garlic taste.

Fries: Voodoo fries live up to its name with a very interesting and nice fries with the sauce. Very easy make you full
I bought the 6 bones meal with a large ranch n one cheese but i dont received the large ranch.. i paid extra for that so im really upset.

I went to this outlet 2 times and the workers there always forget my cup , when I ask for the cup they talk loudly , When I want to talk to them they are always at the back and no one at the counter. The same 2 Person always forgetting my cup and my fork .

First-time try at this stall today for dinner and this is by far the best boneless chicken I had compared at other outlets before, the flavours are more savoury and the chicken appears to be very crispy and piping hot to eat.  Looking forward to another visit here.

We really appreciated the great service and welcoming staff. The staff were very helpful and provided outstanding service. We had a wonderful experience thanks to the excellent service and friendly staff Maam Chona. She even went on our table to check if everything is good. Until our next wing stop!! Will definitely come back.
